title: nasus main looking for duo
body: In S2, I have a 70% win rate with nasus, although dealing with 4 other kids on my team gets difficult at the best of times. I don't use a mic, just need someone else half decent to play with and climb. I never ff, play till the end, don't bother msging me if u give up half way through or flame after a loss.

replies.body:
I'd be willing to duo. We can play later if you're not busy.

At the moment I mainly play support sion.
